{"type": "article", "id": 2427, "title": "眼镜收纳袋", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-18T07:52:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232422oemBnWjbOL5AiS2I.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t戴眼镜的朋友们或多或少会碰到找不到眼镜布的情况，法国包袋品牌 Côte&amp;Ciel 日前联手德国著名眼镜品牌 MYKITA 推出了一款眼镜收纳袋，细心地将眼镜清洁布缝制在了收纳袋地内侧，以免遗失。这款收纳袋由氯丁橡胶制成，安全的厚度为不慎掉落提供了保障，经过特殊处理的拉链也免去了刮花镜面的风险。提供 12 中配色可选，定价 38 美元，<a href=\"https://mykita.com/en/collaborations#layer:/en/projects/cote-ciel\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232420rMOuGcwb6Wx3eEoL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7484375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232421JPWyin2jDF3k1SXY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7484375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232422vFQ4XTzKJUHL3Ypc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7484375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}